content: What happened? This used to work last year

Will not work with note 20 ultra app doesn't create directories needed in data file used to be great but now all things that made it good as a stand alone app have been removed give access to other storage directories please I have paid multiple times from uoyabause first installment all the way through the name change and there again through a 2nd name change where all functions such as loading your own bios adding cheats etc... Other apps have no problem with those features on google play...
Very good with most games
need cheat option

It's a very good emulator with high compatibility but not very accurate to the hardware. My only real issue is with the touch controls, haptic feedback would be a good feature to add in future updates.

While this runs games well, no controller I've tried to use works for the direction pad. I've tried both controllers made for phones and hooking up a ps4 and xbox controller via USB and nothing works, and the key mapping functionality doesn't work. If that ever gets fixed this is a solid 4 star.

I couldn't get a stable fps even with lower resolution rendering and frameskipping on my realme 3. I guess saturn is harder to emulate than dreamcast because redream actually runs better on my phone. Can't say it's good app until it can at least run a single rom without framerate issue

It works, though I understand why a lot of people are upset. The emulator works as it's advertised, I did get it during the devs sale which made it even more worth but for those who lost access to the first version I feel for them. Overall though the app works well and as intended. Hopefully it doesn't get taken down like the first one.
perfect. didn't really expect this to work this smoothly, but it did. Hopefully a fast forward function is added like the other emulators. Anyway, keep up the good work!
This app was a waste of money The free version runs so much better and reads roms much smoother than the pro version please don't bother Wish I could get a refund
Please implement all the features from previous version.
Playing Mystaria right now working great so far.
Street Fighter Alpha 2 , Mortal Kombat Trilogy , X-Men vs Street Fighter and more works well on my galaxy S20 also works well on my nivida shield this is a good Sega Saturn Emulator Great Job!!

Can't Map controller keys. I had a previous version of this and it was working fine. All of sudden my controller stopped working. I can browse the interface but when it comes to mapping the in game controls, the emulator won't register my keys. That makes this emulator unplayable. My controller works with every other android emulator so I'm not sure what v the problem is. I opted to buy this version on Google hoping to fix this to no avail. Yaba Sanshiro get your Shiro together!

Unable to select directory and unable to direct boot games unless in CHD format. Very strange decisions. My game controller stopped working in the old version and now doesn't work on this version. Good Saturn emulator shame about the decisions the dev makes.
First covid, now this app is all screwed. I'm going to go live in the mountains.
Works great, the author should find a way to give those who had paid for the old pro version of the app a free upgrade
I have the old version on this phone which allows me to select a directory, but this new version tells me my version of android doesnt support this...
paid for it. missing the cheat option. but i get why.
Buying this to support the dev who got screwed over by Google and had everyone who bought the emulator left without the license. Great that the dev is running the discount as well.
Sorry your app got removed for stupid reasons but kind of you to lower the price for a few weeks so those of us that bought it can get it for cheap.

Author discontinued yaba sanshiro, changed the name and published it again. Users who had paid for the pro version lost their license and have to pay again for this version. No respect for customers. The emulator is great though.
